This paper is a draft of an article published in Cryptologia by Terry Ritter:

      Ritter, T.  1991.  The Efficient Generation of Cryptographic
      Confusion Sequences.  Cryptologia.  15(2): 81-139.  

The files:
RNG.ps: main article
table.ps: tables of the article
crng2.art: the article in Word 5.1 format
crng2a.fig: the tables in Word 5.1 format
-Aggelos Keromitis (kermit@csd.uch.gr)
